reynard
=======

reynard is a hardened, stealth-focused fork of Camoufox, which is itself a
patched build of Mozilla Firefox (Gecko). It is distributed under the Mozilla
Public License 2.0 (see LICENSE), the same license as its upstreams.

Upstream attribution
--------------------
- Camoufox — https://github.com/daijro/camoufox  (MPL-2.0)
  reynard inherits Camoufox's anti-fingerprinting patch set (navigator, screen,
  WebGL, WebRTC, audio, fonts, timezone, locale, …) and its build tooling.
- Mozilla Firefox / Gecko — https://www.mozilla.org  (MPL-2.0)
  The browser engine being patched.

