the Camoufox project, or any browser/OS vendor.

Bundled fonts are NOT redistributed
-----------------------------------
Upstream Camoufox bundles proprietary OS fonts (macOS / Windows / Tor-Browser
Linux sets) under bundle/fonts/ for font-fingerprint coherence. Those payloads
are copyrighted by their respective vendors and are intentionally OMITTED from
this public repository. See bundle/fonts/000_README.txt for how to supply them
from an upstream Camoufox release before building a font-coherent persona.

Purpose
-------
reynard exists for authorized security testing — letting a security-research
agent operate on consenting / in-scope targets without being misclassified as a
headless bot. It is defensive tooling, not a means to defeat protections on
systems you are not authorized to test.
